positioning

1. static
	- all elements are assigned by default.
	- elements show up top to bottom left to right 
		in the flow of the document.
2. absolute
	- positions the element at x,y coords
	- takes the elemnt out of the flow of the doc
3. relative
	- positions the element relative to where it shows 
		up in the flow

4. fixed
	- positions the element at x,y coord
	- take element out of the flow of doc

position: static;